{
  "stem": "4963.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The-- the mother was home, and she cooked every day and baked and various things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- however--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't have any false paper because no one knew that I was there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I stayed there for six months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- as I said, I-- I was in the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could walk around in the house, but any time someone would knock on their door I would immediately go into that closet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they had no bathroom inside, so I would sit there and with my legs crossed if I had to go for a bowel movement until the nighttime, when I could go out into the outhouse.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And again, they would have to go out and survey all the area, that nobody was around at the time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I would go out and, you know, have my bowel movement and go back into the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But again, I didn't-- I don't think that there were many days when I cried about my-- my-- my life, even though I had such a-- I was brought up with such a spoiled and with a golden spoon in my mouth.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I-- [INAUDIBLE] I took everything as though it's there and what am I going to do to survive, to better myself?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, why do you think this family took you in?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think that they were a really outstanding humanitarian people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the time, I felt that perhaps it was as a payoff for the piano, which the children were also playing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They weren't very wealthy people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just plain folks, farm folks.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
